{"type":null,"faqId":32889,"title":"使用流光快门的光绘涂鸦模式怎样能拍出较好的效果","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">建议在黑暗的房间或者晚上无光源的室外场景拍摄，由一人绘制光绘另一人拍摄。若要将光绘者拍摄出来，可以设置闪光时间，看到即将闪光的提示后光绘者保持静止，即可得到一张光绘者与光绘的合影。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1086,"faqType":"相机与图库","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"7609","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Camera-Gallery","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1436748440000,"seriesProductName":"PLK-AL10,PLK-CL00,PLK-TL00,PLK-TL01H,PLK-UL00","visitedTimes":3,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"相机,流光快门,光绘涂鸦,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}